{"type": "article", "id": 26348, "title": "老旧大楼改造成的办公空间，一个中庭调动了活泼气氛", "description": "就像俄罗斯方块一样拥有无限变化和一颗游戏心。", "date": "2016-05-04T07:10:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4026, "name": "荷兰"}, {"id": 27121, "name": "Studioninedots"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 197, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702141659tW2XawcoHUbejSNi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>中庭往往是一幢大楼最核心的地方，它帮助整幢楼的采光，也能成为视觉的焦点。商场的中庭挂满了宣传广告，而在办公楼里，它也不失一个交流沟通的好地方。</p>\n<p>这处位于荷兰 Hilversum（希尔弗瑟姆）的办公楼是从一个 1970 年代的建筑改建的，它原本属于通信公司阿尔卡特-朗讯（Alcatel-Lucent），现在由房地产公司 De Alliantie 接管。方盒子一样的混凝土建筑看起来严谨而有些生硬，再加上灰暗的色调，已经成为老旧工厂的象征。</p>\n<p>荷兰的建筑事务所<a href=\"http://www.studioninedots.nl/index\"> Studioninedots </a>最明显的改动就是在盒子建筑的中间打开了一个中庭，五层楼的建筑里每一层楼空缺的面积不一样。建筑表面就可以看到这种大面积的玻璃像俄罗斯方块一样堆在一起，中断了长条形窗户的秩序感，也给予空间本身良好的采光。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141648yuUek9piMfz5QWNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141648c0D2oahFMeXJfzLV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>室内部分也如建筑外表一样是错位的，拿走多余的地方和墙面后显得宽敞而明亮。黑色的铁制楼梯连接了每一层楼，与混凝土的梁柱一起构成相互交错的结构，这两种工业材料在这里也拥有了时尚的面貌。</p>\n<p class=\"\">此外，他们还在混凝土横梁上安装了白炽灯以强调这种线条感，阳光从玻璃窗进来穿过层层镂空的梯子让这里显得轻盈而自由。</p>\n<p>“我们通过之字形的结构（zigzags）设计了这些灯光和跳跃的空白，创造出比起单独的直立的天井更多更有趣的连接。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141649O3JTzAd5FZDYQeRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141650j9SaCK4lubcyEMfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">每一层楼的天井和周边区域都有不同的功能，一楼正对着正门口，在楼梯旁有一个接待处，后面有大的会议室。二楼、三楼分别有餐饮储藏室、图书室和会议室，到了四楼和五楼后也有作为一个展示空间。设计者将这些原本分离的区域揉进了中庭的周围，建立了一个集中社交的地方，想要以此鼓励更多的人沟通交流。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">在室内搭配上他们更多使用木板材料，小房间的隔断、天花板吊顶和家具都采用了浅色的木头，让整体空间显得居家，彩色的吊灯点缀其中，这种活泼的装饰风格也挺符合年轻人的审美。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141652Jy19utRG8cQS7KNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141652X7ixfaPUnGOmCr1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141653y6V3W5OwEbI1vBh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54237288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141653xoLkfNUw1y27uFWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一楼大厅</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141654CqDI9uw1Yc7fyaLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一楼大厅</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141654nqhNP1g8f93YXLv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">二楼</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141655ZXb0AJySonvlICTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141655Zb9RhT5LcX2e6szK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141656vHnMbZB5WlDgAQKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021416567OZVCbnQRrtL13jm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141657qKNG3pJHEnmhIoTc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021416579D8QjoZhqpncwxgl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.338\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141658fYtVcCe79jF8x5NG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.338\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141658lXWewxJUjpZsha25.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.338\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141659kGvBwAtV1Wbn6fMi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.338\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/30/studioninedots-de-alliantie-headquarters-office-hilversum-netherlands-concrete-steel-staircases-atrium/\"> dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.studioninedots.nl/index\">Studioninedots</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n\n\n"}